The <strong><code>DOMPointReadOnly</code></strong> interface specifies the coordinate and perspective fields used by <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPoint" title="A DOMPoint object represents a 2D or 3D point in a coordinate system; it includes values for the coordinates in up to three dimensions, as well as an optional perspective value."><code>DOMPoint</code></a> to define a 2D or 3D point in a coordinate system.